>The screwed-up mission rosters...how can they be 
>circumvented??? I can't find a way....

There are two ways to deal with this problem;

1:  The best way is to prevent it from happening.  Quite simple really... what
is happening is that the game keeps track of the 'mission number' you are
currently on (and displays that one and the next three).  Unfortunatly if you
go to the bottom of the list (say mission #22) and then fly to a port without
many missions (say 15) you are now at a mission that does not exist.  The
solution should be obvious... always go to the first mission on the list before
leaving a port.

2:  If you forgot to go to the top of the list at your last port all is not
lost.  The game resets the missions every day, and thus also resets you to the
first mission on the list.  Simply hit accelerated time until the next day
comes and you will have a mission list... but you've lost a day.
