Down in the Imperial region there are alot of mining colonies that produce
slaves as a major export.  You can fly from one to the next and fill all your
holds with slaves... and then fly to one of the Terraformed Imperial worlds
that have slaves as a major IMPORT.  Then if you go to the bulletins menu and
find someone who needs slaves desperately and will pay double... well, the sum
is truly staggering.  BTW, a good spot for this is a cluster of planets down
and to the right of Achenar (still in Imperial space though).  Don't remember
any names because I haven't been over that way in about 4 years of game time.
