In the message * Frontier Contracts (again!) * Graham  wrote:

 GJ> I would love to hear from anybody who has succeeded in fulfilling their

I've fulfilled a few. Go to the place you were told when you got the contract.
Be SURE to be on time! Just before the time you were given, launch, and wait.
At the exact time, your target will leave the spaceport/station, and hyperjump.
Use your hypercloud analyzer to determine where he's gone, and then follow him.
You MUST have a light ship, so that you get to the target system in advance
of your target. Once there, target his arrival cloud (will appear long before
your target does!), and wait.

If there is no arrival cloud, and if he doesn't appear within minutes of the
designated time, he's made a misjump to evade you, and is impossible
to find.

