Now, to carelessly reply to my own post... Just booted up Frontier.
Used the wormhole bug to go to the vicinity of Beta Lyrae; if it's
supposed to be difficult to get to the outskirts of the galaxy, then
this should DEFINITELY be fixed, as with it, you can just cheat your
way around the problems of running out of fuel, drive servicing,
misjumps, and fuel scooping. Beforehand I'd stripped down my Constrictor,
filled it with military fuel, and three large jumps from the "wormhole"
