Elite (original) on a 1200? Well when I got my first 1200 back in Jan of
this year, Elite worked fine...no need for turning off caches or using
Degrader. But it had problems with the hard drive fitted that caused 
colour problems. So a few months later when I finally got a newer 1200,
I tried to play Elite.....and it refused to load!

Just recently I tried again using degrader and experimenting with the
startup options, and found that I could in fact load it simply by
turning caches off, disabling all drives except df0: and using ECS chips.

So maybe everyone has been right, and it just depends exactly when your
1200 was made?

	John

